data.meta_description: 1904 High Uintas Ln, Heber City, UT 84032 is a single-family home listed for rent at $4,500 /mo. The 3,300 Square Feet home is a 5 beds, 4 baths single-family home. View more property details, sales history, and Zestimate data on Zillow.
data.text: Brand New Beautifully 5 Bedroom Home with Breathtaking Views of the Wasatch Back! Welcome to your dream rental in Heber! This stunning, brand new home offers a luxurious living experience. With 5 spacious bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms, and 3200 square feet of living space, this home is perfect for families, professionals, or anyone seeking to live in the beautiful Heber Valley. Home to come furnished or unfurnished depending on lease length. Beautiful kitchen with gas oven and range. Quartz countertops. Master on the main level with walk in closet and it's own washer and dryer unit. Spacious downstairs entertainment area with pool table, smart TV and sectional. 4 of the 5 bedrooms have their own walk in closet. 4 smart TVs throughout the home. Varying lease lengths are available, 1 year preferred. Please reach out with questions. Pets are allowed with a pet fee. 1 gps Wi-fi, electricity, and garbage included in price. Renter to cover water and gas. 2 car garage for parking. No smoking allowed.
